@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #222222
skinparam ArrowFontColor #000000
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  FontColor #000000
  BorderColor #000000
}
title SDK Utils Before parseBooleanFlag Export

package "athena-js SDK" {
  rectangle "src/index.ts\n(public export surface)" as Index #F5F5F5
  rectangle "src/auxiliaries.ts\n(error/result/int/retry helpers)" as Aux #E8F4FF
}

rectangle "Consumers\n(apps, scripts, test-sdk)" as Consumers #FFF7E8

Index --> Aux : re-exports existing helpers
Consumers --> Index : import helpers from SDK
Consumers ..> Aux : no shared parseBooleanFlag utility

note bottom of Aux
Missing shared parser for string
boolean flags in env/CLI contexts.
end note
@enduml
